content: I'm considering trading in my Toyota Corolla for a newer model, but I want to get some quotes for insurance first. Can you help me compare rates from different providers? By the way, I recently got a parking ticket because I misunderstood the parking rules - I was parked in a 2-hour spot, but it was only valid until 6 pm and I got there at 5:45 pm, so I ended up staying for 3 hours.
